snippet.title: Bionic Bay Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Spring Showcase 2025
snippet.description:
A new gameplay trailer introduced us to the atmospheric biomechanical world of Bionic Bay, a speedrunning platformer with competitive multiplayer. The game is coming soon to PC and PlayStation 5, but in the meantime, a new demo is available on Steam.

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#FutureGamesShow #FGS #bionicbay 

Future Publishing uses the Epidemic Sound Library and Adobe Creative Cloud Generative AI features
